# OTWPO 
This is the official implementation for "OTWPO".

## Installation

To run the code of OTWPO, first create a virtual environment using e.g. conda:
```bash
conda create -n otwpo python=3.10
```

Activate the created environment, and install pytorch `v2.1.2` based in your hardware according to [Pytorch Installation Page](https://pytorch.org/get-started/previous-versions/), e.g.:
```bash
pip install torch==2.1.2
```

Install the specific `alignment-handbook` version via:
```bash
pip install -e .
```

Install Flash Attention 2:
```bash
pip install flash-attn==2.5.5 --no-build-isolation
```

Install the rest packages by running
```bash
pip install -r requirements.txt
```

Finally, log into your huggingface account by:
```bash
huggingface-cli login
```

